ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDags.name: ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDags
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDags.description: Fetches detailed metadata for a specific DAG.
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDags.returns: A promise that resolves to the DAG detail object.

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagRuns.name: ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagRuns
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagRuns.description: Fetches DAG runs for the given DAG ID and Google Cloud Project.

parameters.name: gcpProjectId
parameters.description: The Google Cloud Project ID where the Composer environment lives.

parameters.name: dagId
parameters.description: The ID of the DAG to fetch runs for.

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: The maximum number of runs to fetch. (Defaults to 20)

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskInstances.name: ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskInstances
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskInstances.description: Fetches all task instances for a specific DAG run.

parameters.name: dagRunId
parameters.description: The ID of the specific DAG run.

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskInstances.returns: A promise that resolves to an array of task instance objects.

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskLog.name: ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskLog
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskLog.description: Fetches the raw log for a specific task attempt.

parameters.name: dagRunId
parameters.description: The ID of the DAG run.

parameters.name: tryNumber
parameters.description: The attempt number of the task.

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchTaskLog.returns: A promise that resolves to the raw log content as a string.

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagDetails.name: ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagDetails
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagDetails.description: Fetches detailed metadata for a specific DAG.
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchDagDetails.returns: A promise that resolves to the DAG detail object.

ComposerAirflowClient_fetchAirflowConfig.name: ComposerAirflowClient_fetchAirflowConfig
ComposerAirflowClient_fetchAirflowConfig.returns: A promise that resolves to the Airflow configuration object.
